Thank you.

01:39:06.910 --> 01:39:10.650
So welcome back our next
panel is called documentaries,

01:39:10.650 --> 01:39:13.010
style and the use of archives.

01:39:13.010 --> 01:39:15.560
And Pat Aufderheide
will moderate.

01:39:15.560 --> 01:39:18.420
Pat is a univeristy professor
of communication studies

01:39:18.420 --> 01:39:21.000
at the school of communicationat
American University

01:39:21.000 --> 01:39:22.540
in Washington DC.

