And my seniors are
wathicng American

03:14:00.460 --> 03:14:05.040
Experience Documentaries.

03:14:05.040 --> 03:14:09.960
But I - I - you can use
these documentaries to teach

03:14:09.960 --> 03:14:11.570
about narrative structure,

03:14:11.570 --> 03:14:14.650
since they use narrative
structure we just ehard.

03:14:14.650 --> 03:14:17.010
You can teach them
about media literacy,

03:14:17.010 --> 03:14:19.990
which I think is
really important skill

03:14:19.990 --> 03:14:23.610
that they are not coming
to college with these days,

03:14:23.610 --> 03:14:26.820
and we need it more than ever.

03:14:26.820 --> 03:14:30.820
So there are creative ways

03:14:30.820 --> 03:14:35.830
to use these programs beyond
simply the formal education

03:14:35.830 --> 03:14:39.530
or informal education that
they were designed for.

