of optimism about public
broadcasting and it's future

03:15:34.180 --> 03:15:36.150
and it's potential in that way.

03:15:36.150 --> 03:15:38.960
But I welcome your
thoughts about this.

03:15:38.960 --> 03:15:41.910
&gt;&gt; Paula Apsell: I was
going to say one thing is

03:15:41.910 --> 03:15:46.120
that I think we just talked
a minute or so about age.

03:15:46.120 --> 03:15:51.120
I mean the hope is that the
American public will demand the

03:15:51.120 --> 03:15:52.920
preservaiton of public media.

03:15:52.920 --> 03:15:55.700
You know we have to
have our fans out there.

03:15:55.700 --> 03:15:59.580
They are our biggest asset,
and I think many of you

03:15:59.580 --> 03:16:05.440
in this room remember under
few years ago, decades ago,

