03:16:17.230 --> 03:16:20.680
That is our prservation,
that is our guarantee.

03:16:20.680 --> 03:16:24.770
So the concern I have is
yes indeed we want to expand

03:16:24.770 --> 03:16:26.830
and get younger people.

03:16:26.830 --> 03:16:30.830
Listen I love my older
viewers, keep watching.

03:16:30.830 --> 03:16:36.260
Oldies but goodies, I love
you okay, don't stop waching.

03:16:36.260 --> 03:16:38.390
People are living
longer and longer.

03:16:38.390 --> 03:16:40.050
So it's great.

03:16:40.050 --> 03:16:43.470
We do want to get younger
people but we also want to get,

03:16:43.470 --> 03:16:45.380
I know this is near
and dear to your heart.

03:16:45.380 --> 03:16:47.600
We want to get more diversity.

03:16:47.600 --> 03:16:53.500
Not just because we're ethical
people, but also becauase

03:16:53.500 --> 03:16:58.480
that is our survival, the
