03:16:58.480 --> 03:17:00.360
and we have to change with it.

03:17:00.360 --> 03:17:07.430
And my job is to really find
ways to - and choose topics

03:17:07.430 --> 03:17:12.890
that show people sceince
belongs to you, not just to me.

03:17:12.890 --> 03:17:18.440
Listen sicence has been
white, we all know that.

03:17:18.440 --> 03:17:23.150
It's changing it's bringing
many more minoritis into it.

03:17:23.150 --> 03:17:25.450
We used to tear our
hair out to try

03:17:25.450 --> 03:17:28.220
and find minority scientists
to put on the screen.

03:17:28.220 --> 03:17:33.080
Now it's really - you know in
some fields it's chalelnging

03:17:33.080 --> 03:17:37.360
but in many it's really not
hard at all That's great.

03:17:37.360 --> 03:17:41.570
So one way is to really make
sure that we have scentists

03:17:41.570 --> 03:17:45.960
of all different colors and
all different backgrounds

03:17:45.960 --> 03:17:47.260
on the screen.

03:17:47.260 --> 03:17:50.560
Another way is in the choice
of topics that we have

03:17:50.560 --> 03:17:57.140
to choose topics that take
into account people's concerns.

03:17:57.140 --> 03:18:00.410
And so hopefully this is not
something that's going ot

03:18:00.410 --> 03:18:01.710
be accomplished.

